official_title: A bill to amend the act of August 30, 1890, to except a tract of ground located in Carbon County, Wyoming, from its restrictions.

summary.text: (Reported to Senate from the Committee on Interior and Insular Affairs with amendment, S. Rept. 94-821) Conveys to the record owner named in this Act all right, title, and interest of the United States in specified lands in Carbon County, Wyoming.

titles.title: A bill to amend the act of August 30, 1890, to except a tract of ground located in Carbon County, Wyoming, from its restrictions.
